title: SWERVE  [Arcana Studios 2012] complete
description:
Arcana Studios Presents -    "SWERVE" 01-06 [Complete] (Digital)(2012)

San Antonio, 1976: Eric Layton, desperate for cash, left college behind to dive into the world of pro-wrestling. From there, it was an easy slide into the underbelly of the "rasslin'" biz, where the box office and concession stand make for an easy way to launder drug money. 

Writer: Jon Judy
Artist: Dexter Wee
Publisher: Arcana Studio
Release Date: October 17, 2012

Thanks goes to all storytellers involved and the original scanners.
 (Zone-Empire) (Son Of Anarchy-Novus)
